thread.title: thanks to all who participated

comments.text: i know i've said this a few times but i just want everyone to know i'm happy to have so many people want to get involved or at least show interest in such a short time period...
... everone who has even attempted to contribute has each shown a unique take on the theme which turned out to be much more interesting than what i had in mind...
...despite most contributors 'not finishing their builds', i am still greatfull for your efforts. i only wish for people to enjoy their time on anyland with whatthey want to do.
i will continue to add minor tweeks to the solar system for a better experiance when i have the time.
